Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:08.82,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Care to let me run\Nin front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:11.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:12.82,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:18.83,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:18.83,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.78,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nabikanai nagasarenai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.78,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give in. I won't be dragged away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:24.01,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima kanjiru koto ni sunao de itai no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:24.01,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay honest to the way I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:24.72,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:24.72,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:26.83,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nando demo umarekawaru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:26.83,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be reborn as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.78,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kanashimi mo dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.78,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my sadness with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:31.41,J,,0000,0000,0000,,hashiridasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:31.41,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:39.85,J,,0000,0000,0000,,tanoshii uragiri ni atte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:39.85,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, betrayal can be pleasurable...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:43.15,J,,0000,0000,0000,,torawarenai atashi ga koko ni iru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:43.15,E,,0000,0000,0000,,But I stand right here - not giving in to temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:45.54,J,,0000,0000,0000,,tarinai tsukinai nandatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:45.54,E,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enough," "not enough," whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:47.64,J,,0000,0000,0000,,motto hizumasete yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:47.64,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:51.50,J,,0000,0000,0000,,pataan kashita konna sekai ja
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:51.50,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Living in this routine-laden world...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.52,J,,0000,0000,0000,,jibun ga dare nano ka wakaranakunaru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.52,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...is enough to make you forget who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:57.71,J,,0000,0000,0000,,waku ni hamaritakunai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:57.71,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be stereotyped...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:01:01.84,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kimetsukenaide yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:01:01.84,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...so don't make assumptions about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:05.60,J,,0000,0000,0000,,michi naki michi wo yuku no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:05.60,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to blaze my own trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:09.00,J,,0000,0000,0000,,soko ni itatte matteitatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:09.00,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will ever be accomplished...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.89,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nani mo hajimaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.89,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you just stand around waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:12.63,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:12.63,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.80,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nabikanai nagasarenai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.80,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give in. I won't be dragged away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.40,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima kanjiru koto ni sunao de itai no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.40,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay honest to the way I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.40,0:01:23.30,J,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no omoidoori ni wa sasenai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.40,0:01:23.30,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:24.31,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:24.31,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:26.57,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nando demo umarekawaru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:26.57,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be reborn as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:28.54,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kanashimi wo dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:28.54,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my sadness with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:32.08,J,,0000,0000,0000,,hashiridasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:32.08,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:33.72,J,,0000,0000,0000,,anata no moto ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:33.72,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm past the point of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:37.77,J,,0000,0000,0000,,mou kaerenai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:37.77,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot go back to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:39.70,J,,0000,0000,0000,,atashi wa atashirashiku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:39.70,E,,0000,0000,0000,,On my own terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.27,J,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.27,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wanna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:00.22,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, you piece of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.68,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you cut my leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.68,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you, you damn bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:17.03,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:20.57,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,So you can punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.67,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,That last one only\Ngave me an itch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:25.08,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were\Nsome giant fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:29.79,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to hit me, do it\Nwith all your might, maggot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:34.86,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,You're an impudent little fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:11.20,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll skip the explanation of what\Ngoes into a Garganta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:14.21,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,If you go the other way, you'll get\Nto the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.58,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.26,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to watch\Nyour footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.69,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,One misstep inside, and\Nyou'll wind up in some
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:28.78,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,unknown space between the World\Nof the Living and Hueco Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.60,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:34.56,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that would provide some\Ninteresting data as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.15,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:44.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, when\NMr. Urahara saw us off,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,he talked to us from\Na high place too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:02.59,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:06.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're the second Chief of\NResearch and Development,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.28,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,you must have been Mr. Urahara's\Napprentice or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.56,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You two are kind of similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.02,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.36,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:18.15,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Isane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:20.65,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.86,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,I will, Captain Unohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.06,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:37.33,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.42,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki is a\Nfascinating man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.26,B2,NEMU,0000,0000,0000,,Master Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.43,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be interesting\Nto trap him in the Garganta,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.39,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,but I changed my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.72,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.64,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,putting some fear into him\Nonce this battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:59.61,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Fear that'll make him think of this\Nbattle as a pleasant memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.38,B2,NEMU,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Master Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.57,B2,NEMU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think up a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.88,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,For a worm, you're pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:21.34,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.26,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.26,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Can't fight back anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:34.14,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:37.56,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you like a damn fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.67,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! My finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:50.91,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you cut off my finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:04.40,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.89,B2,YAMMY (OFF),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You damn bug!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:18.89,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stay behind,\NMayuri Kurotsuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.19,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,How odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:24.82,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't seem like something\Nyou'd care to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.17,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,There should be more\Nthings that are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:30.55,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,of interest to you in the\NWorld of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:35.83,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,So why stay here?\NWhat are you plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:39.29,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? How very cautious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.27,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:45.30,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not planning anything\Nthat'll scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:53.13,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that, at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:56.24,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,the corpses over here\Nare more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.23,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.68,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Once the battle in the World\Nof the Living is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:04.19,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,someone will open up a Garganta\Nfrom the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:10.47,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use that to go to the\NWorld of the Living,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:13.66,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,and take my time to examine\Neach of the corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:17.83,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.62,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:25.13,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you, what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.84,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,If you have something\Nto say, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.09,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.05,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:36.28,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected you\Nto say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.01,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,I was a little surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:40.02,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.48,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,That thing you just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.44,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded as if you were implying\Nthat sending Ichigo Kurosaki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.86,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,to the World of the Living\Nwould end the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:58.19,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded as if you believed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.87,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,that Ichigo Kurosaki\Nwould be victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:09.78,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:12.52,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Absolute nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:17.97,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected such words to come\Nfrom you, Byakuya Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.90,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.44,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.89,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.95,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,You encountered Sosuke Aizen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.91,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,at the Sokyoku Hill\Nonce before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:49.92,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.87,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't much\Nto think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.88,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,He had monstrous strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.87,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even use his Shikai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:31.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It was a one-sided battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:34.94,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,"He didn't even use his Shikai."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.47,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Did I hear that correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:39.61,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.57,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:42.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:46.64,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you had such\Na large difference
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.77,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,in strength was your\Ngreatest fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:55.44,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,I shall tell you now, Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:10:00.41,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, you are probably\Nthe only person
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:04.37,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,in the World of the Living, Soul\NSociety and Hueco Mundo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:07.33,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,who can fight Sosuke Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:09.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.00,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,I shall tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:16.40,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,about the powers of his Zanpakuto,\NKyokasuigetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.52,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,and the requirements\Nfor activating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:36.23,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Zanpakuto,\NKyokasuigetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:39.00,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Its ability is complete hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.09,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Complete hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:46.43,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,But the Kyokasuigetsu is\Na water-type Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.24,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,It confuses your enemies\Nand makes them
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.83,B2,ISAEN,0000,0000,0000,,attack each other by using\Nreflections created
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.20,B2,ISAEN,0000,0000,0000,,from mist and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:54.66,B2,ISAEN,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you told us,\NCaptain Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:57.60,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,You gathered us Lieutenants together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:00.13,B2,ISAEN,0000,0000,0000,,and demonstrated it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.09,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.85,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,So that was actually\Nthe hypnosis ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.39,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:13.72,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Complete hypnosis dominates\Nall five senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:16.89,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,It can cause everything about\Na target, including its form,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:24.01,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,shape, mass, feel, and even smell,\Nto be mistaken for an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:27.48,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it can make\Na fly appear to be a dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:30.50,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,or a swamp appear to\Nbe a field of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.54,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to activate it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:39.46,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,is to show my enemies my\NKyokasuigetsu's release.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.90,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who sees it, even once,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:45.54,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,falls under complete hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:49.84,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,From then on, complete hypnosis\Ntakes hold of them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.98,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,whenever I release\Nmy Kyokasuigetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:56.44,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who sees\Nit...even once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:57.88,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:01.36,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Thirteen Court\NGuard Squads,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.06,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke Urahara's men,\Nwith whom you are
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:06.37,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,acquainted with in the\NWorld of the Living,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:10.81,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,as well as Sosuke Aizen's\Nsubordinates,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.76,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,the Arrancars and\Nthe Espadas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:18.25,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who is possibly\Ninvolved in the battle in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:21.21,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,the World of the Living has\Nseen Aizen's Shikai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.68,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:27.59,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.85,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,You possess a Spiritual Pressure\Nthat rivals that of a captain
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.65,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,and you have not seen the\NKyokasuigetsu's Shikai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.12,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So as long as I don't\Nsee Aizen's Shikai,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.56,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I won't fall under his\Ncomplete hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.54,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:47.66,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Your advantage is very\Nimportant in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.98,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,No. More accurately,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:57.58,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,if you lose that advantage,\Nthis battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.07,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.10,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens\Nin this battle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:05.65,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,from here on out, do not look\Nat Sosuke Aizen's Shikai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.05,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.18,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.98,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Unohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:17.34,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I heard that before\NI went into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.98,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that is more\Nthan enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.16,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:27.57,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:32.83,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,You're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:45.33,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that itches,\Nyou worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:04.29,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? His brain isn't the only\Nthing brutish about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.36,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,If he's able to knock that\Ngiant body into the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.24,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,he's got some brute\Nstrength in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.98,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:13.70,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,You're starting to really\Npiss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.85,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,I am so pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:19.99,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Damn bug! You damn bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:32.59,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,But if he's going to defeat him,\NI wish he'd do it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.81,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dying to dissect\Nthat Espada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.23,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,It appears
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:51.61,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be dissecting the Squad 11\NCaptain before the large one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.39,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,That should be enjoyable too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.34,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.26,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,They are severely injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.34,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,But I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.80,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Please save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:11.83,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:17.72,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.87,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:36.03,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Care to let me run\Nin front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.83,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about my Spiritual\NPressure consumption,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.28,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be... fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:43.74,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:47.17,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Care to let me run\Nin front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.13,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.09,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:56.05,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.71,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:03.64,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,The path looks so\Nnice when done
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,by a captain's Spiritual\NPressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.98,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, the difference is so great\Nthat it's making me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:11.43,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.45,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,We're no different in terms\Nof Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:15.53,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:20.08,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,From what I can see, your\Nwounds have healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:23.26,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you were making a mess\Neven in your best condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.33,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Your sloppy Spiritual Pressure\Nis just not suited
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.92,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,for this sort of task.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Sloppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:30.71,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:32.19,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,If my Spiritual Pressure were\Ncompletely recovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.38,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I could do a little better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:37.85,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,You look a little too awake\Nto be daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.18,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.45,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're\Nbeing a little mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:43.85,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not daydreaming, or joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:46.16,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I only have a right sleeve, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:53.78,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,When I do Bankai,\Nmy Shihakusho changes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.00,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.95,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,this transformed Shihakusho
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.48,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,is also part of my Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:11.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,As proof of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:14.51,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,When Inoue healed\Nmy wounds earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.40,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,only part of my\NShihakusho was fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:22.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Normally when Inoue heals me,\Nit'd fix my Shihakusho as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.39,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So I asked her why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:32.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Inoue can\Nheal wounds quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.86,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,but it takes her a while to revive\Na person's Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:40.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But Rukia and the others were\Nin trouble, so I hurried off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:43.33,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I went off without having my\NSpiritual Pressure restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:47.33,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So this is all the Spiritual Pressure\NI have right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.92,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,If I were at my best,\NI could do better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:53.96,B2,UNOHANA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:59.27,B2,UNOHANA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His Shihakusho is less than\Nhalf of what it usually is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.97,B2,UNOHANA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does that mean that he only has\Nhalf of his Spiritual Pressure?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:04.97,B2,UNOHANA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was under the\Nimpression that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:09.85,B2,UNOHANA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}his Spiritual Pressure rivaled\Nthat of a captain at his best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:19.45,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, you should\Nrun in the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.88,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to restore your\NSpiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:25.87,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,as best as I can while\Nwe're on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:30.03,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,On the move? While\Nwe're running?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.38,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:32.62,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.42,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,When healing with Kido,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:38.02,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,we start by restoring one's\NSpiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.17,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,The restored inner\NSpiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:45.35,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,and the healer's external Spiritual Pressure\Nthen heal the body itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:46.82,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:51.24,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, restoring\Nthe Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.31,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,in a body that has been\Nhealed is quite easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:56.28,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Please move to the\Nfront, Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.95,B2,UNOHANA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this really is only half\Nof his Spiritual Pressure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:14.26,B2,UNOHANA (M),0000,0000,0000,,He may really be\Nour trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.50,B2,UNOHANA (M),0000,0000,0000,,Someone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.56,B2,UNOHANA (M),0000,0000,0000,,who can end this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.78,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.70,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me,\Nyou damn bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:47.34,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.60,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.08,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:59.92,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,M-My leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:09.42,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I was getting\Ntired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:12.96,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I almost fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.98,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,But now it looks like I\Ncan begin dissecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.75,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Nemu, prepare to dissect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:20.48,B2,NEMU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.77,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,He finally went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.41,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:34.33,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you done, big guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:41.25,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Byakuya Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:43.21,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,He's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.97,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you handle the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.93,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what\Nyou mean by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:49.97,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.95,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,You must be bored from\Nwatching all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.70,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:57.02,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm letting you take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:58.68,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:03.53,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to clean up\Nafter your unfinished job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.28,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.03,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:10.29,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like finishing off those\Nwho are weaker than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.45,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.52,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.05,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Finishing someone off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:20.29,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,is a job that is suited\Nfor a brute like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.30,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.27,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:32.64,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:35.44,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:56.84,J,,0000,0000,0000,,koe sae ushinattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:56.84,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I was stripped of my voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:03.64,J,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa koko de utau darou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:03.64,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be here, singing my song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:11.18,J,,0000,0000,0000,,koko kara hibike
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:11.18,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Echo out from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:19.98,J,,0000,0000,0000,,miminari ni kesareta seijaku no yoru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:19.98,E,,0000,0000,0000,,The ringing in my ears stole the night's tranquility.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:26.92,J,,0000,0000,0000,,katachi nai mirai wo oikaketeta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:26.92,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I chased a future that doesn't exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:34.08,J,,0000,0000,0000,,sono te wa kuu wo tsukandekita kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:34.08,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet all I caught was nothing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:37.72,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to it! Listen to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:41.67,J,,0000,0000,0000,,deai ga tsumuideku merodi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:41.67,E,,0000,0000,0000,,The melody of the people we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:45.08,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! Listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:47.97,J,,0000,0000,0000,,oto ni kawaru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:47.97,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...as I become sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:57.16,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa mada konna ni chiisa na kono koe ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:57.16,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Though my voice is still small and meager today...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:03.69,J,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka wa tsuyoku hibiiteiku kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:03.69,E,,0000,0000,0000,,One day it shall gloriously resound.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:07.32,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to it! Listen to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:11.16,J,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashiku yuriokosu merodi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:11.16,E,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweet melody that'll awake\Nyou from your slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:14.60,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:19.91,J,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2800)}kimi ga omou kimi e
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:19.91,E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2800)}My song will reach the person you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:23.31,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing Unohana, with your\Nskilled healing powers and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:24.47,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Why, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.47,0:23:26.05,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Must come with age, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:28.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Unohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:32.47,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,It's shameful for a man to talk\Nabout age in front of a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:33.80,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:34.80,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:36.60,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to\NSoul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:39.62,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.62,0:23:42.69,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I feel like I'm\Nforgetting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:45.67,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Something that starts\Nwith "Hana"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:46.15,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:47.32,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:48.24,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:48.92,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:49.42,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:49.96,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:50.33,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:50.89,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:51.69,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:53.28,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Megane (Funny Glasses)!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:54.54,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:58.64,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,I can't seem to concentrate\Non the job without this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.64,0:24:00.75,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's continue on\Nwith the treatment!
